strings: <voice_0x01001C8C><se_high>media princess: I spent the day thinking about what I should say next spring.
<voice_0x01001C8D><se_high>media princess: But we have a lot to share. Sometimes I don't know where to start...
<voice_0x01001C8E><se_high>media princess: It was a pleasure traveling with you <hero>.
<voice_0x01001C8F><se_high>media princess: unless he is a horse
